snippet.title: Beer - Business As Usual Amber Beer From Derby Brewing  Co -- Review #2193
snippet.description:
Heres a new beer for me from Derby Brewing Co, brought from Asda locally, heres a Description "A balanced easy drinking, malty, traditional amber beer. SIBA Midlands Regional Gold Winner.  " for me an outstanding malty beer, the taste has to be believed.

#derbybrewingco #amberbeer #beer #beerreview
